•   promote the dissemination of advanced technology related to the design and construction of  wooden buildings; 

 •   develop human resources with knowledge and skills related to the design and construction  of mid to high-rise wooden buildings or large-scale wooden buildings; 

 •   provide information on the safety of architectural timber and wooden structures; 

 •   promote the system of agreements to promote the use of wood in buildings (see below); 

 •   rationalize the building standards; 

 •   promote the use of timber for government buildings; and  

 •   ensure the quality of timber and stable supply.
